				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"2ef17e5e-152e-4a27-87a6-4181ed37aecc\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"bodily-decay\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Bodily Decay</tooltip> talent or <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"eroding-escape\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Eroding Escape</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"b44ab6d5-0003-4dd7-bdff-624ef586cb1e\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"07649ae6-f09f-438c-9a18-c33030d0e689\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You annihilate your targets from a distance by sending your entropic spark racing through a physical object, creating a chain reaction at its destination.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"838a7be8-e8ab-4f13-90f6-4cb2a49806c3\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">You can use Division and its talents as though your <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reach\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">reach</tooltip> is 20 feet, as long as there is a solid surface from you to your target (such as a wall or floor) along which you can send an entropic spark.</p>",
