				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"fb2be769-fa25-45e3-9129-c13abbb8f0d9\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"spark-sending\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Spark Sending</tooltip> talent or <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"gout-of-flame\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Gout of Flame</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"45bb4096-923e-443f-9162-6b0e20ee2d99\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"072921d1-b2e4-4f47-abc0-4530ef118567\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve grown so powerful that the ability to destroy everything around you is almost alarmingly easy.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"c5359832-3921-4918-aa8c-8fba1e078a15\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">It costs you one <span aria-label=\"One Action\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"One Action\">▶</span> fewer to use Division (but not its talents). Additionally, your DCs on the <a href=\"/nexus/cosmererpg/sources/stormlight-handbook/chapter-6-surges/#DivisionUnderPressure1\" title=\"Division Under Pressure\">Division Under Pressure</a> table are reduced by 5.</p>",
